<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p><strong>Welcome to the PlanetTalk Admin Portal!</strong></p>

<p>You've been added as an admin. Use the details below to log in and set your new password.</p>

<div class="credentials-box" style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #24B6C3;">Your Login Credentials</h3>
    <div class="credential-item">
        <strong>Email:</strong>
        <span class="credential-value">{{email}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="credential-item">
        <strong>Temporary Password:</strong>
        <span class="credential-value">{{temporaryPassword}}</span>
    </div>
</div>

<p>Go to <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="color: #24B6C3; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">{{loginUrl}}</a> to log in. You'll be asked to create a new password right away.</p>

<p>Need help? Contact <a href="mailto:agent@planettalk.com" style="color: #24B6C3; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">agent@planettalk.com</a></p>

<p>Cheers,<br><strong>The PlanetTalk Team</strong></p>

